WEBVTT

00:02:59.335 --> 00:03:00.694
kosmološke konstante,

00:03:00.694 --> 00:03:03.451
budućim svemirom
će sve više dominirati

00:03:03.451 --> 00:03:04.592
tamna energija,

00:03:04.592 --> 00:03:06.330
a on će postajati sve hladniji

00:03:06.330 --> 00:03:08.715
i širiće se sve brže.

00:03:08.715 --> 00:03:10.736
Na kraju,
svemir će ostati bez gasa

00:03:10.736 --> 00:03:11.842
za pravljenje zvezda

00:03:11.842 --> 00:03:13.941
i same zvezde će ostati bez goriva

00:03:13.941 --> 00:03:15.192
i ugasiće se

00:03:15.192 --> 00:03:18.062
ostavljajući samo crne rupe u svemiru.

00:03:18.062 --> 00:03:19.255
Uz dovoljno vremena

00:03:19.255 --> 00:03:21.610
čak i ove crne rupe će ispariti

00:03:21.610 --> 00:03:24.523
i ostaviti potpuno hladan
i prazan svemir.

00:03:24.523 --> 00:03:28.127
To je ono što zovemo
toplotna smrt svemira.

00:03:28.127 --> 00:03:29.569
Iako možda zvuči depresivno

00:03:29.569 --> 00:03:30.694
živeti u svemiru